  <div class="comment-content">
    <div class="author"><div class="picture">
  <a href="/users/spine001" title="View user profile."><img src="http://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/pictures/picture-76111.jpg" alt="spine001&#039;s picture" title="spine001&#039;s picture"  /></a></div>
</div><div class="author"></div>
    <p>If you own, lets say 10 million usd equivalent of gold. And you keep it in a vault you pay storage and aadministrative fees. But if you deposit in a bank's vault, then you can use the certificate of deposit as collateral for a loan and if you are able to invest that loan at lets say 10% per year, you make 100,000.00 usd per year rather than paying storage fees. That is why Corzine had so much gold in his control. The risk is ibvious, you can get Corzined!</p>
<p>But that is why Countries have kept gold in SWITZELAND, USA and LONDON</p>

