</div><div class="author"></div>
    <p>Money must be</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span>1. General Acceptability</span><br /><span>2. Portability</span><br /><span>3. Divisibility</span><br /><span>4. Cognizable</span><br /><span>5. Homogeneity or Uniformity</span><br /><span>6. Durability</span></p>
<p><span>7. Preserves buying power.</span></p>

